Vonage-Click2Call version 0.10
==============================

Use the Vonage™ Click-2-Call third party interface (see https://secure.click2callu.com/) to
place a call from your Vonage line to another party.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 LWP::UserAgent (with SSL support)

